description:
The Protestant Reformation restored much Biblical truth to the world. And while persecution drove many Reformers from Europe, God continued to correct doctrinal errors and guide His people toward greater truth. In this presentation, Pastor Water Veith looks at how some widely held Protestant doctrines continue to erroneously affect our views of God. See why having a right understanding of the character of God is a vital, life-and-death issue.
